➜茶清香、籽醇香！《从长江的尽头回家》安庆潜山直播专场香气十足！
http://www.sohu.com/a/433960830_118040	21684
<p><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201124/86264ff187854ac8b1ac271a1819bc19.png" /></p>
<p><strong><span><span>昨晚六点整</span></span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>《从长江的尽头回家》</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span><span>安庆潜山好物直播专场</span></span><span>，</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span><span>在江苏卫视快手官方直播间</span></span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span><span>如约而至</span></span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span><span>本期的好物推荐官有</span></span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>主持人刘仪伟、</span></strong><strong><span>演员姜潮</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>和我们熟悉的主持人彭宇</span></strong><span></span></p>
