<p><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>一</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">“皖”</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>好物</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">，“陶”</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>气十足</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">！</span></strong></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>首先登场的是痘姆古陶纯手工高温素陶竹节杯</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>古典高雅的竹节杯一登场</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>立刻成为全场的焦点</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>好物推荐官将竹节杯拿在手里</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>隔着屏幕都可以感受到它的分量</span></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201124/c17a58df09004807a9706367020d8906.gif" /></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>不愧是用天然陶土和紫砂制作的杯子</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>厚实的胎体使竹节杯具备很强的保温性</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>用来泡茶</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>养人养神</span><span>还能时刻保温！</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>直播间还现场展示了痘姆龙窑的照片</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>好山好水出好土</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>好土陶冶出竹节杯</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>陶艺爱好者千万不要错过</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>！</span></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201124/0e22b1e25a20493b949a2d29389efe36.gif" /></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">“进窑一色，出窑万彩”</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>光听这介绍就足够令人好奇</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>第二位上场的</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>就是绝对独一无二的土陶罗汉杯</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>直播现场展示的四个杯子</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>各有特色</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>独特的釉色在光照下更加晶莹剔透</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>试问谁不想拥有这份独特的美丽呢</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>！</span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201124/dbce6c60f72b492594ea704478cc5254.png" /></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>模样质朴的红陶煲</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">使用价值是当仁不让的第一名</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>炖</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>、</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>煮</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>、</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>熬</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>、</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>烧样样行</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>高温烧制有保障</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>看到红陶煲</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>在座的好物推荐官就自然联想到美食</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>红陶煲炖鸡汤是安庆当地的一大特色</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>你是不是已经垂涎三尺了呢</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>？</span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201124/4289a5fc032d440d830570bc5bfe7c1a.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>宅家首选</span></span></strong></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>来安庆不吃瓜蒌籽怎么行</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>！</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>安庆的房前屋后</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>田间地头</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>都是种植瓜蒌籽的好地方</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>不愧为</span>“瓜蒌之乡”！ </span></p>
<p><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201124/5fcc0a1e4dc94452b919e763946840d8.png" /></p>
<p><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201124/00a3e75df11a4e2aba7c8a66e35c0b01.png" /></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>直播间一共介绍了两款瓜蒌籽</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>跨越瓜蒌籽和天柱山瓜蒌籽</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>奶油味瓜蒌籽香香甜甜、皮薄肉大</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>不仅富含钙、铁等人体所需的微量元素</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>而且还不易上火</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，吃了也不易发胖，</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>绝对是宅家首选零食</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>直播间里还没吃过的观众，趁着优惠快来下单！</span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201124/c450ecf02a724657b17e10820e59e15a.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>茶香安庆</span></span></strong></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>被誉为</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;">“中国十大名茶”之一的天柱剑豪</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>外形似剑</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>、</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>内有白毫</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>好物推荐官介绍</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>天柱剑豪的产量有限</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>一芽一叶的采摘与制作都极其讲究</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>生产一斤茶叶要用到三万颗芽头</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>绝对是茶中精品</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>！</span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201124/2c86b2e5b1c54e30a3045ee98a011c2c.png" /></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>现场泡一杯茶</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>可见茶汤</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>色泽碧透</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>、</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>热气氤氲</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>隔着屏幕都能闻到茶香</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>！</span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201124/a8752a6839794b4d8c28f78f1d911c7f.gif" /></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>黄金芽被誉为</span>“茶中大熊猫” </span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>直播间展示泡好的茶汤</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>明黄透亮</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>色如黄金</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>黄金芽的采摘期短</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>所以更加金贵</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>品一口</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>不苦不涩</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>满嘴飘香</span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201124/f667d0f12b4b46e990d7ddfe411f3a6f.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>健康搭档</span></span></strong></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>不饱和脂肪酸、不含胆固醇</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>山茶油和亚麻籽油可以说是</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>健康好搭档</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>无污染</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>无添加</span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201124/524dfa1ea8c6428d9b4bd87c977bd8c9.png" /></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>采用低温物理冷榨工艺萃取</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>宝宝吃、孕妇用</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>无论是炒、煎还是炸</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>每一滴都是放心油！</span></span></p>
